comments: Great teacher, she is very friendly and a fair grader. Make sure to turn assignments in on time, she does not always accept them late, and then means 5 minutes after she asks them to be turned in. You can tell she is very passionate about what she teaches, and will assign readings weekly. Keep up, show up, and you\'ll be fine.
